{"tid":1948612,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"到今時今日，外國留學生先係攬炒派最大功臣","createTime":"2020-03-29T06:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T09:10:36.000Z","uid":213877,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1317e9e5812e62ae91c1f75b1c617b93628e99","tid":1948612,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"仲屌乜鳩留學生？手足黎嫁，無佢地，日日個案會激增 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留學生先係攬炒派最大功臣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLJLjK1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLJLjK1.gif&h=dc956b0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec2113767ebc6112382a31ef621899a8523da5bb","tid":1948612,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎疫情持續，由昨日（28日）下午4時至今，至少新增36宗初步確診個案，與酒吧相關的感染群組佔13宗，其中8宗涉及中環蘭桂坊Insomnia等4間相關酒吧。截至昨日下午4時，酒吧群組已增至54人感染，連同其後的初步確診個案，恐至少67人中招。<br />\n<br />\n輸入個案方面，一名由英國返港的14歲男子，懷疑將病毒傳染給父母和胞弟；其父親為早前確診的第467號患者，沒外遊，3母子則初步確診。14歲大仔3月15日由英國返港，11歲細仔沒外遊，與47歲媽媽同在東區醫院留醫。另外，至少3名初步確診者是空中服務員。<br />\n<br />\n此外，一名居於元朗博愛醫院楊晉培護理安老院的90歲長者，首次檢測的鼻咽樣本不肯定是否陽性，痰液樣本則呈陰性，要再抽取樣本化驗，正等候結果，未屬初步確診個案。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200329/H7AWJOVSH3BESCLUPSBROXEY3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200329%2FH7AWJOVSH3BESCLUPSBROXEY3A%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe9LD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=48095931\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200329%2FH7AWJOVSH3BESCLUPSBROXEY3A%2F&h=1ed29d87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200329/H7AWJOVSH3BESCLUPSBROXEY3A/</a>"},{"pid":"dff9be799db51074ec7f8663f91d2bb8833088e1","tid":1948612,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"笑撚死，係緊屌藍絲紅底外國留學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4ffcf04e91e907c9da208370eca96fee41da80","tid":1948612,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:48:47.000Z","msg":"三罷終於已經做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c425d01eb58d617f4935e84e842443c728c98cb4","tid":1948612,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"攬炒巴d手足黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5cb31788c529bbca4a9fa4019ad4deb0f063f6","tid":1948612,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecb366f5d720a87aadf3aeec26de46b0359efb5","tid":1948612,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:10:06.000Z","msg":"始終連登仔就係錫身怕事<br />\n口講攬炒但做就另一套<br />\n係都要 777 做野攬炒"},{"pid":"c13ce8ec4698fc3af5dfa2543efafa02d71f72a4","tid":1948612,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}